To source the current file in VIM
:source ~/.vim/.vimrc

Install exuberant ctags for tagging purpose
ctags -R .
run the above command in terminal from the root folder of project and it will create a tag file
And this tag file is read by vim for tagging
Ctrl-] 
on tag name in vim
g Ctrl-] 
list all tag names in vim
Ctrl-t 
jump several times over tags deep into source
